window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p> <b>With the threat on Tanila's life, Max gives into the black skill: Consume.</b> </p> <p> It has evolved, and the destruction it brought was glorious, frightening, and overwhelming.</p> <p> Now, with the new growth and power that came with it, Max and the others find themselves once again fighting against difficult odds as they make a push to get strong enough to reach the tower. </p>"; 
